It was all a mess on Tuesday night's episode of Please Step In as Ma Angie tried to dissect the mess that unfolded on screen between Nthabiseng and her mother Leah. Leah was concerned and upset when her daughter and the man who barely raised her daughter excluded her from lobola negotiations. Leah approached the show to intervene, but once Ma Angie had scratched the surface of the relationship, all kinds of skeletons were revealed. From learning that malume had paid lobola but not damages, to revelations of him impregnating his ex, it was a lot. He had apparently "helped" his ex out, after she couldn't fall pregnant in her new marriage. It was a proper mess! The best part was when Leah was acting dramatic and the internet was sure she was a 50-year-old slay queen. The people came with the memes: